t: OTRERA - Amazon Queen of Greek Mythology
s: In Greek mythology Otrera was the first Amazon queen and a bride of the war-god Ares. She was also the founder of the celebrated shrine of Artemis at Ephesus. Otrera was probably the unnamed Amazon queen who battled the hero Bellerophon in Lycia and the Trojan King Priam in Phrygia.
